sentences: Sir Shina Peters (born 30 May 1958) is a Nigerian Jùjú musician.
Shina Peters, after releasing many albums with Segun Adewale through the 1980s, went on to form his own band, "Sir Shina Peters & His International Stars".
Sir Shina Peters and his International Stars released their first album Ace (Afro-Juju Series 1) in 1989.
The album went on to garner awards for Peters including the artist and album of the Year at the Nigerian Musical Awards.
Sir Shina Peters currently has 16 album releases to his credit.
